g this <http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/lrn.st?>     Here are more\nreads we picked out to get your wheels turning <http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/lrn.st?>\n=== Do You Know the Story behind These Iconic Photos? ===\n\n Ashley Lauren Dickinson <http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/lrn.st?> === The Simpsons\nafter 26 Years ===\n\n Steve Webb <http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/lrn.st?> === 4 Types of Steals You Can Get\nwith a Student ID ===\n\n Lauren Kelly\n\n\n\n    Share your knowledge with others With every bit you learn you can teach\nothers. On learnist, we provide a platform that helps others share their\nknowledge. After all, the best way to learn is to teach others.\n\n\n Share your knowledge <http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/lrn.st?>\n                 Try Learnist on your Android or iOS device\n<http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/play.google.com?p=eyJzIjoiOWNKb3BFQ3ZCSi04aGJZWXBzbXBKNzdEZDBJIiwidiI6MSwicCI6IntcInVcIjoxMTAwMTY1OSxcInZcIjoxLFwidXJsXCI6XCJodHRwczpcXFwvXFxcL3BsYXkuZ29vZ2xlLmNvbVxcXC9zdG9yZVxcXC9hcHBzXFxcL2RldGFpbHM_aWQ9Y29tLmxlYXJuaXN0XCIsXCJpZFwiOlwiMDM1ZGI1NjQ1ZDYyNDk3ZmI5MmE4ZGVkYTc1Nzc0YzVcIixcInVybF9pZHNcIjpbXCJhZGEyYzFiZjNlZWYwMDI0NzAzYjJiNTdmMmNmMjc3YTU2MDIyYjU1XCJdfSJ9>\n<http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/itunes.apple.com?p=eyJzIjoiYkw3TTZHLWZETnRYbllPeUxmTVdnZExaZDhnIiwidiI6MSwicCI6IntcInVcIjoxMTAwMTY1OSxcInZcIjoxLFwidXJsXCI6XCJodHRwczpcXFwvXFxcL2l0dW5lcy5hcHBsZS5jb21cXFwvdXNcXFwvYXBwXFxcL2xlYXJuaXN0LXdvcmxkcy1rbm93bGVkZ2VcXFwvaWQ4MjY1OTExNzU_bXQ9OCZ1bz00XCIsXCJpZFwiOlwiMDM1ZGI1NjQ1ZDYyNDk3ZmI5MmE4ZGVkYTc1Nzc0YzVcIixcInVybF9pZHNcIjpbXCJlNDVhYmE1MTM5MGQzNjQ4NWYwY2E4ZTA0OWUwNTQ1NjIwZDljNTJkXCJdfSJ9>\nDon't want to receive email notifications? Adjust your message settings\n<http://mandrillapp.com/track/click/11001659/learni.st?>.\n\n Learnist values your privacy and does not make your email address\navailable to any other third party without your permission.\n\n \u00a9 2014, Learnist Inc. 500 3rd Street Suite 260, San Francisco, CA 94107\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\" style='margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'>\n<head style='margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'>\n  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" style='margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'>\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width\" style='margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'>\n  <style style='margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'>\n    /* -------------------------------------\n    \t\tGLOBAL\n    ------------------------------------- */\n    * {\n    \tmargin:0;\n    \tpadding:0;\n      font-family: \"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\n    }\n\n    img {\n    \tmax-width: 100%;\n    }\n    .collapse {\n    \tmargin:0;\n    \tpadding:0;\n    }\n    hr {\n      width: 100%;\n      height: 1px;\n      margin: 0 auto 10px;\n      border: none;\n      background-color: #ccc;\n    }\n    hr.small {\n      width: 95%;\n    }\n    .block {\n      display: block;\n    }\n    .inline-block {\n      display: inline-block;\n    }\n    .center {\n      text-align: center;\n    }\n    .avatar {\n      max-width: 125px;\n      height: auto;\n      border-radius: 2px;\n    }\n    .margin-top {\n      margin-top: 15px;\n    }\n    .bold {\n      font-weight: 600;\n    }\n    .app-link {\n      font-size: 14px;\n      color: #ccc;\n      font-weight: 500;\n    }\n      .app-link a {\n        color: #ccc;\n      }\n    .grey {\n      color: #666;\n    }\n    .icons {\n      display: inline-block;\n      margin: 2.5% 0 5%;\n      height: 40px;\n    }\n      .icon-image {\n        width: auto;\n        height: 40px;\n      }\n    .float-left {\n      float: left;\n    }\n\n    body {\n    \t-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;\n    \t-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;\n    \twidth: 100%!important;\n    \theight: 100%;\n    }\n    /* -------------------------------------\n        OTHER RECOMMENDED BOARDS\n    ------------------------------------- */\n    .content-box-other-recommended {\n\n    }\n      .other-recommended {\n        float: left;\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 30%;\n        margin: 0;\n        padding: 0 0 0 2.5%;\n        color: #666;\n        vertical-align: top;\n      }\n        .other-recommended-img {\n          width: 100%;\n          border-radius: 3px;\n        }\n        .other-recommended-h4 {\n          min-height: 35px;\n          margin: 5px 0;\n          color: #444;\n          font-weight: 400;\n          font-size: 14px;\n          overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .other-recommended-p {\n          text-transform: uppercase;\n          color: #888;\n        }\n\n    /* -------------------------------------\n        ELEMENTS\n    ------------------------------------- */\n      .mail-body {\n        background-color: #EEE9E7;\n      }\n\n\n    a {\n      color: #00AFEC;\n      text-decoration: none;\n    }\n\n    .btn {\n    \ttext-decoration:none;\n    \tcolor: #FFF;\n    \tbackground-color: #666;\n    \tpadding:10px 16px;\n    \tfont-weight:bold;\n    \tmargin-right:10px;\n    \ttext-align:center;\n    \tcursor:pointer;\n    \tdisplay: inline-block;\n    }\n\n    p.callout {\n    \tpadding:15px;\n    \tbackground-color:#ECF8FF;\n    \tmargin-bottom: 15px;\n    }\n    .callout a {\n    \tfont-weight:bold;\n    \tcolor: #2BA6CB;\n    }\n\n    table.social {\n    /* \tpadding:15px; */\n    \tbackground-color: #ebebeb;\n\n    }\n    .social .soc-btn {\n    \tpadding: 3px 7px;\n    \tfont-size:12px;\n    \tmargin-bottom:10px;\n    \ttext-decoration:none;\n    \tcolor: #FFF;font-weight:bold;\n    \tdisplay:block;\n    \ttext-align:center;\n    }\n    a.fb { background-color: #3B5998!important; }\n    a.tw { background-color: #1daced!important; }\n    a.gp { background-color: #DB4A39!important; }\n    a.ms { background-color: #000!important; }\n\n    .sidebar .soc-btn {\n    \tdisplay:block;\n    \twidth:100%;\n    }\n\n    /* -------------------------------------\n    \t\tHEADER\n    ------------------------------------- */\n    table.head-wrap {\n      width: 100%;\n      background-color: #fff;\n    }\n\n    .header.container table td.logo { padding: 15px; }\n    .header.container table td.label { padding: 15px; padding-left:0px;}\n\n\n    /* -------------------------------------\n    \t\tBODY\n    ------------------------------------- */\n    table.body-wrap {\n      width: 100%;\n      margin-top: 1%;\n    }\n\n\n    /* -------------------------------------\n    \t\tFOOTER\n    ------------------------------------- */\n    table.footer-wrap { width: 100%;\tclear:both!important;\n    }\n    .footer-wrap .container td.content  p { border-top: 1px solid rgb(215,215,215); padding-top:15px;}\n    .footer-wrap .container td.content p {\n    \tfont-size:10px;\n    \tfont-weight: bold;\n    }\n    .footer-wrap-column {\n      width: 70%\n    }\n\n    /* -------------------------------------\n    \t\tTYPOGRAPHY\n    ------------------------------------- */\n    h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6 {\n    font-family: Helvetica, \"HelveticaNeue-Light\", \"Helvetica Neue Light\", \"Helvetica Neue\", Arial, \"Lucida Grande\", sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom:15px; color:#000;\n    }\n    h1 small, h2 small, h3 small, h4 small, h5 small, h6 small { font-size: 60%; color: #6f6f6f; line-height: 0; text-transform: none; }\n\n    h1 { font-weight:200; font-size: 44px;}\n    h2 { font-weight:200; font-size: 37px;}\n    h3 { font-weight:500; font-size: 24px;}\n    h4 { font-weight:500; font-size: 21px;}\n    h5 { font-weight:500; font-size: 18px;}\n    h6 { font-weight:500; font-size: 16px; margin-top: 15px;}\n\n    .collapse { margin:0!important;}\n\n    p, ul {\n    \tmargin-bottom: 10px;\n    \tfont-weight: normal;\n    \tfont-size:14px;\n    \tline-height:1.6;\n    }\n    p.lead { font-size:17px; }\n    p.last { margin-bottom:0px;}\n\n    ul li {\n    \tmargin-left:5px;\n    \tlist-style-position: inside;\n    }\n    .small-text {\n      font-size: 11px;\n    }\n    .body-text {\n      font-size: 17px;\n      line-height: 1.5;\n    }\n\n    /* -------------------------------------\n    \t\tSIDEBAR\n    ------------------------------------- */\n    ul.sidebar {\n    \tbackground:#ebebeb;\n    \tdisplay:block;\n    \tlist-style-type: none;\n    }\n    ul.sidebar li { display: block; margin:0;}\n    ul.sidebar li a {\n    \ttext-decoration:none;\n    \tcolor: #666;\n    \tpadding:10px 16px;\n    /* \tfont-weight:bold; */\n    \tmargin-right:10px;\n    /* \ttext-align:center; */\n    \tcursor:pointer;\n    \tborder-bottom: 1px solid #777777;\n    \tborder-top: 1px solid #FFFFFF;\n    \tdisplay:block;\n    \tmargin:0;\n    }\n    ul.sidebar li a.last { border-bottom-width:0px;}\n    ul.sidebar li a h1,ul.sidebar li a h2,ul.sidebar li a h3,ul.sidebar li a h4,ul.sidebar li a h5,ul.sidebar li a h6,ul.sidebar li a p { margin-bottom:0!important;}\n\n\n\n    /* ---------------------------------------------------\n    \t\tRESPONSIVENESS\n    \t\tNuke it from orbit. It's the only way to be sure.\n    ------------------------------------------------------ */\n\n    /* Set a max-width, and make it display as block so it will automatically stretch to that width, but will also shrink down on a phone or something */\n    .container {\n    \tdisplay:block!important;\n    \tmax-width:600px!important;\n    \tmargin:0 auto!important; /* makes it centered */\n    \tclear:both!important;\n    }\n      /* This should also be a block element, so that it will fill 100% of the .container */\n      .content {\n      \tdisplay:block;\n        max-width:600px;\n        padding:15px;\n      \tmargin:0 auto;\n      }\n        .content-box {\n          position: relative;\n          padding: 20px 30px;\n          border-top: 1px solid #D2D2D2;\n          border-right: 1px solid #D2D2D2;\n          border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;\n          border-left: 1px solid #D2D2D2;\n          border-radius: 2px;\n          background-color: #fff;\n        }\n        .has-header {\n          border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;\n        }\n        .has-footer {\n          border-radius: 0 0 2px 2px;\n        }\n        .has-header-and-footer {\n          border-radius: 0;\n        }\n        .content-box-header {\n          max-height: 0;\n          padding-bottom: 56.67%;\n          border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;\n          overflow: hidden;\n        }\n          .content-box-header-image {\n            display: block;\n            height: auto !important;\n            max-width: 600px !important;\n            width: 100% !important;\n            border-radius: 2px 2px 0 0;\n          }\n        .content-box-footer {\n          padding: 20px;\n          border-left: 1px solid #D2D2D2;\n          border-right: 1px solid #D2D2D2;\n          border-bottom: 1px solid #D2D2D2;\n          border-radius: 0 0 3px 3px;\n          background-color: #eee;\n        }\n          .button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            padding: 10px 20px;\n            border: 1px solid #6DC023;\n            border-radius: 3px;\n            background-color: #73CB01;\n            color: white;\n            font-size: 17px;\n            font-weight: 500;\n            text-align: center;\n            letter-spacing: .5px;\n          }\n          .button-off {\n            border: 1px solid #bbb;\n            background-color: #ccc;\n          }\n          /* BOARD STUFF */\n          .board-title {\n            padding-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 28px;\n            font-weight: 300;\n            color: #000;\n          }\n          .board-curator-box {\n            height: 55px;\n            overflow: hidden;\n          }\n            .board-user {\n              border-radius: 50%;\n            }\n            .board-curator {\n              margin-top: 2.5px;\n              margin-left: 65px;\n              font-size: 17px;\n            }\n          .board-img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n          }\n\n    /* Let's make sure tables in the content area are 100% wide */\n    .content table { width: 100%; }\n\n\n    /* Odds and ends */\n    .column {\n    \twidth: 300px;\n    \tfloat:left;\n    }\n    .column tr td { padding: 15px; }\n    .column-wrap {\n    \tpadding:0!important;\n    \tmargin:0 auto;\n    \tmax-width:600px!important;\n    }\n    .column table { width:100%;}\n    .social .column {\n    \twidth: 280px;\n    \tmin-width: 279px;\n    \tfloat:left;\n    }\n\n    /* Be sure to place a .clear element after each set of columns, just to be safe */\n    .clear { display: block; clear: both; }\n\n\n    /* -------------------------------------------\n    \t\tPHONE\n    \t\tFor clients that support media queries.\n    \t\tNothing fancy.\n    -------------------------------------------- */\n    @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {\n\n    \ta[class=\"btn\"] { display:block!important; margin-bottom:10px!important; background-image:none!important; margin-right:0!important;}\n\n    \tdiv[class=\"column\"] { width: auto!important; float:none!important;}\n\n    \ttable.social div[class=\"column\"] {\n    \t\twidth:auto!important;\n    \t}\n    }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"mail-body\" style='margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\", \"Helvetica\", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;width:100%;height:100%;background-color:#EEE9E7;'>\n  <table class=\"head-wrap\" style='margin:0;padding:0;font-family:\"Helvetica Neue\